        <desc>This piece by Banksy appeared in Los Angeles in 2006 and clearly pokes fun at the large numbers of girls on MySpace who used flattering angles and photo editing to make themselves appear more attractive. 
            It shows it from the old lady with the comment ‘You Looked Better on Myspace’.</desc>
